1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,050
A scene of pure joy. A healthy, vibrant young girl runs through a hospital hallway, her laughter echoing as she leaps into her father's arms.

2
00:00:05,050 --> 00:00:20,050
Lin Feng holds his daughter close, his face, so often a mask of cold fury, now completely transformed by a smile of profound love and relief. This small, precious life is the center of his universe, the reason for his fight.

3
00:00:20,050 --> 00:00:35,050
His loyal subordinate appears, delivering a final, quiet report. The Zhang family, the source of so much pain, has been dealt with. Their empire is dismantled, their power extinguished. Justice has been served.

4
00:00:35,050 --> 00:00:45,050
Lin Feng's gaze drifts towards the window, his expression growing distant and somber. His thoughts travel back in time, back to the origin of his pain, to the wound that has never truly healed.

5
00:00:45,050 --> 00:01:15,050
And now, we see the truth. Through a series of stark, painful flashbacks, the real story is revealed. We witness the betrayal, the corporate sabotage orchestrated by the Zhang family that led to the ruin of Lin Feng's own parents, a tragedy that shattered his world and set him on this long, dark path of vengeance.

6
00:01:15,050 --> 00:01:30,050
His voice, now a solemn narration over the images of the past, confirms the depth of his resolve. This was never just about a recent insult. This was a decade-long promise, a vow made to his fallen family that he would one day reclaim their honor.

7
00:01:30,050 --> 00:01:45,050
A doctor approaches, but not to discuss a patient. He bows deeply to Lin Feng, expressing immense gratitude. He speaks of a new medical wing, a beacon of hope for countless other children, funded by a massive, anonymous donation.

8
00:01:45,050 --> 00:01:57,050
Holding his daughter, Lin Feng looks at this new legacy. A faint, genuine smile touches his lips. The cycle of revenge is over, replaced by a cycle of healing. He has transformed his pain into a force for good.

9
00:01:57,050 --> 00:02:12,050
The camera slowly pulls back. Father and daughter stand together, bathed in the warm sunlight pouring through the hospital window. Behind them, a new building stands tall, a symbol that his victory was not just an end, but also a new beginning.
